description:
Tenma Gabriel White, known as Gabriel or Gab for short, is an angel who was the top of her class but turned into a good-for-nothing slacker after becoming addicted to anime and video games. She is often lazy and unmotivated and has a rather bossy attitude.
Gabriel came to Earth to attend a human high school and learn about humans after graduating for her Angel School in the upper world.
name: Tenma Gabriel White
